ur worksheet.  " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 31 "1.  Graphing functions an
d the " }{TEXT 257 4 "plot" }{TEXT -1 89 " command.  The Maple command
 for plotting the graph of an explicitly defined function is:" }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 5 "     " }
{TEXT 258 0 "" }{TEXT 259 4 "plot" }{TEXT 260 0 "" }{TEXT -1 2 "( " }
{TEXT 261 4 "expr" }{TEXT -1 2 ", " }{TEXT 266 1 "x" }{TEXT -1 20 "=ra
nge [, options]);" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 6 "where " }{TEXT 262 4 "expr" }{TEXT 267 1 " " }{TEXT -1 24 
"is a symbolic expression" }{TEXT 264 1 " " }{TEXT -1 48 "which repres
ents the function to be plotted and " }{TEXT 263 1 "x" }{TEXT -1 38 " \+
is the independent variable used in  " }{TEXT 265 4 "expr" }{TEXT -1 
25 "  to define the function." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}
{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 81 "Several options exist to change way the p
lot will appear.  These options include:" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 
0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 126 "            y=range              \+
         this allows the user to specifiy the range of output values w
hich Maple will display" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 113 "            t
hickness=value           this controls the thickness of the plotted cu
rve.  value = 1, 2, 3, 4, or 5" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 119 "      \+
      color=value                 this sets the color of the plotted c
urve.  value = red, green, blue, cyan, etc." }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
-1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 160 "For each of the following func
tions provide a plot to represent the graph the function.  Choose a ra
nge that will optimally represent the features of the graph." }}{PARA 
0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 16 "a.    y = 3x - \+
1" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 6 "b.    " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "y = 6*x^2+24*
x-8;" "6#/%\"yG,(*&\"\"'\"\"\"*$%\"xG\"\"#F(F(*&\"#CF(F*F(F(\"\")!\"\"
" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 5 "c.   \+
" }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "y = ((1+x)/(1-x))^(1/2);" "6#/%\"yG)*&,&\"\"\"F(%\"x
GF(F(,&F(F(F)!\"\"F+*&F(F(\"\"#F+" }{TEXT -1 1 " " }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" 
{TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 4 "d.  " }{XPPEDIT 18 0 "y = \+
exp(-x^2)/(1+x^2);" "6#/%\"yG*&-%$expG6#,$*$%\"xG\"\"#!\"\"\"\"\",&F.F
.*$F+F,F.F-" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT -1 0 "" }}{PARA 0 "" 0 "" {TEXT 
